abstract: Federal Aviation Admin is investigating near collision between JetBlue passenger flight and small aircraft in skies over Westchester County Airport.
lead_paragraph: Passengers described a near collision of two planes near Westchester County Airport on Sunday, which the Federal Aviation Administration is investigating.
